n memory. A multi-gigabyte audiobook on a low-RAM laptop can crash the tab. If that happens, merge in two passes and concatenate the results.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}]\n32:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-takeaways\",\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-takeaways\",\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Key Takeaways\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"The Audio Merger combines MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC files into a single output.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"circle\",{\"cx\":\"12\",\"cy\":\"12\",\"r\":\"10\",\"key\":\"1mglay\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\",\"key\":\"dzmm74\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-foreground\",\"children\":\"The Audio Merger combines MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC files into a single output.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Optional chapter markers make the merged M4A navigable in audiobook players.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$32:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Optional chapter markers make the merged M4A navigable in audiobook players.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"All processing runs locally via ffmpeg.wasm; files never leave your browser.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$32:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"sp