numeric sorting.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Chapter markers\"}],\" — Each input file becomes a chapter in the output M4A, with the filename as the chapter title.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Multiple output formats\"}],\" — Export as M4A (AAC), MP3, or OGG with bitrate from 64 to 320 kbps.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Mix input formats\"}],\"— Combine MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, FLAC, AAC, and WebM files in the same merge. They're all decoded and re-encoded to your chosen output format.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"100% client-side\"}],\" — Uses ffmpeg.wasm (WebAssembly). Your files never leave your device.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"How to Merge Audio Files\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"1. Add files\"}],\" — Drag and drop audio files into the upload area, or click to browse. You can add files in multiple batches.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"2. Arrange order\"}],\" — Drag files in the queue to reorder, or click Natural Sort to automatically sort by filename.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"3. Choose output settings\"}],\" — Select your output format (M4A, MP3, or OGG), bitrate, and whether to include chapter markers.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"4. Merge\"}],\" — Click Merge and wait for processing. The progress bar shows the current status.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"5. Download\"}],\" — When complete, click Download to save the merged file to your device.\"]}]]}],[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Audio Merger\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Sort by filename before merging audiobook chapters\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],\"$L14\"]}],\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\"]}]]}],\"$L18\",\"$L19\"],\"$L1a\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\"]}]\nd:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/06xqo6ats2teh.js\",\"async\":true}]\ne:[\"$\",\"$L1e\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$1f\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@20\"}]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Sort by filename before merging audiobook chapters\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Browsers don't guarantee selection order. The tool reads filenames to set chapter order, so zero-pad your filenames (Chapter_01.mp3, Chapter_02.mp3 …) and the chapters will land in the right sequence every time.\"}]]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Match the lowest source bitrate when re-encoding\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$c:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Match the lowest source bitrate when re-encoding\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Merging files of different bitrates and then encoding at the highest source bitrate is wasted bytes — the lower-quality chapters can't be upgraded. Pick the lowest input bitrate as your output target.\"}]]}]]}]\n16:[\"$\",\"li\",\"M4A with chapter markers beats one giant MP3\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$c:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"M4A with chapter markers beats one giant MP3\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Audiobook players (Apple Books, Smart AudioBook Player) jump between M4A chapter markers natively. A merged MP3 plays as a single 8-hour track with no navigation.\"}]]}]]}]\n17:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Keep input files until the merge finishes\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$c:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Keep input files until the merge finishes\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"ffmpeg.wasm reads files lazily during the merge — closing the browser tab or moving the source files mid-process aborts the job. Wait for the download prompt before cleaning up.\"}]]}]]}]\n18:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Common Mistakes to Avoid\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Merging files of different sample rates without converting\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\",\"key\":\"wmoenq\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 9v4\",\"key\":\"juzpu7\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 17h.01\",\"key\":\"p32p05\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Merging files of different sample rates without converting\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Mixed sample rates (44.1 kHz + 48 kHz) cause pitch and timing drift. The tool re-encodes to your selected output spec, but quality is best when the inputs are already consistent.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Forgetting to enable chapter markers\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$18:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"childr